@node History

1.3 (22.9.98)
-------------
FIX: quitting Altabber caused a guru when launched from wb.
ADD: active window shown in different color.
ADD: 68020+ version included.


1.4 (11.10.98)
--------------
ADD: now can also cycle through screens


1.5 (1.4.99)
------------
ADD: the window is sized after the longest title to be shown.
ADD: hotkeys not hardcoded but adjustable w/arguments or tooltypes.
ADD: Olivier's Memory Method -- remebers the last selected win/scr so that it's the first to appear.
ADD: if AUTOACTIVATE is on activates the first win of the raised scr.

@endnode

